{"tid":597223,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳冠希上海商演突被拉走","createTime":"2018-03-18T12:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T14:10:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d33f20141aaa680a84fe45ebea2194f809797cb5","tid":597223,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"藝人陳冠希昨日於上海出席商演活動登台，而活動亦有進行網上直播。期間陳冠希接受訪問時，只作了自我介紹，一名男子就突然上前，把他推開並帶走。他當時顯得一臉愕然，而直播亦隨即中斷。事件引來不少揣測，有傳該男子為便衣警員，而陳冠希被帶走是因為沒有商演證件。 <br />\n<br />\n事後，「陳冠希國際聯盟」於微博發言澄清事件：「陳冠希已經平安離開。請各位粉絲不要擔心。」東網聯絡上陳冠希方面表示：「昨天冇乜嘢，好好，佢做佢嘅工作，其他嘢問番客戶。」而陳冠希公司則回應：「為確保現場觀眾的安全，警方建議並果斷要求臨時叫停活動和採訪。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/200639_ae78ed5389c9368c9ef10f503c462e21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F200639_ae78ed5389c9368c9ef10f503c462e21.png&h=a96391d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/200645_a0fec3445f6c7b3bf5e8022726a63ff0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F200645_a0fec3445f6c7b3bf5e8022726a63ff0.png&h=9a41fe38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/200648_d31548a33176b06d7d2bb670773473d0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F200648_d31548a33176b06d7d2bb670773473d0.png&h=e9c42ee2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/200651_bd0ff37cbb00c49edb7a2113f1800d02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F200651_bd0ff37cbb00c49edb7a2113f1800d02.png&h=4005de3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180318/mobile/bkn-20180318162731869-0318_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180318%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180318162731869-0318_00862_001.html&d=Vb%2FYpL6%2Bk2axMqEtcXk0R6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=298edb0f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180318/mobile/bkn-20180318162731869-0318_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a5890a05e755bce9ea36f6f80fc9dd47d528cf5a","tid":597223,"uid":96743,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"錦衣衛出動！ （特殊任務）<br />\n為慶祝習帝登基<br />\n習帝決定與民同樂！<br />\n現派出新東廠錦衣衛尋找從未流出的幻之短片s<br />\n<br />\n目標： 傳說中尚未流出的5條短片<br />\n分別與愛迪生在床上進行激戰的戰鬥片段"},{"pid":"a79b53ce5adeec2327619139207bfcd50e6b9d66","tid":597223,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"東廠"},{"pid":"196a46018f78e1c29a3b5f4f86fb9f7713c4a374","tid":597223,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:03:47.000Z","msg":"可能收到風有痴線佬要隊佢"},{"pid":"dd5141a9d9d3810a63f984a4ea33d6911563eeb5","tid":597223,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:10:33.000Z","msg":"無俾利是姐"}]}